name: BodeGato 003 Name: Pepper
description:
- Anny: We found her in the patio, before the big flood. Remember? She was so little! I just bought her a new collar with really bright colors to contrast her quimera fur. 
— Anny: Ohh! I love her! Onix and Rojo fight over her.. but she isn't interested at all.
—- Anny: The fish behind her? lol I bought her a toy too. Is the $CARI, our token. You know why is called like that? Because of Carite fish 🐟
